      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>A bill to allow State Homeland Security Program grant funds to be used to pay costs associated with the attendance of part-time and volunteer first responders at terrorism response courses approved by the Office for State and Local Government Coordination and Preparedness.</title>
